call Includes/RLNatural

# Visible multi-agent RL stage 6. The scene intentionally contains the superset
# of bodies the reset bridge may address: Herons robot1..robot4 and opponents
# robot21..robot23. Stage 6 only controls players 1 and 2; the others are moved
# by reset requests or B-Human.
ci 30
gc playing
ar kickOffDelay off
ar penalizeIllegalPosition off
ar penalizeIllegalPositionInSet off
